Analyses and Insights¶

At this point, 'WeRateDogs twitter archive' is wrangled through 3 dataframes and later join after cleaning acts to form a master dataframe 'twitter_archive_master.csv'. 
After wrangling and analysis, we found some useful insights about the twitter archive which we will further discuss on. 
some of its findings are: -

  • Common Dog types

  • Top rated dogs

  • common Dog names

  • Top most liked dogs

  • Most retweeted dog

common Dog types¶

  • implementing the value count function of pandas on the dog_prediction column, we can find that the types; 'Pembroke', 'Chihuahua', 'Pug', 'Labrador Retriever' are one of the more common dog types having a use score average of 50 - 90 near a hundred.
  • The most common Dog type is the "Golden Retriever" with a use score of 139. This makes it the most popular dog type in the area.

common Dog names¶

  • __There are lots of names given to dogs, a ton of them even so in this contex but however, the are common dog names that we use or assign to our pets more often than not. Some of the high end number of dogs who bear common / same names; 
       *Lucy*

Top rated Dogs¶

  • We analyzed and can examine from the query of the dog_prediction column that although the Golden retriever may be well known and appretiated dog type, the 'Pembroke' tends to be the highest rated among the dog types with a score count of 4 with the 'French Bulldog' sharing a score of 2 counts with the 'Golden Retriever'.
